DFL7     TITLE 'E X H I B I T  ***  A.M.S. 370 SCREEN LAYOUT MODULE'
EXHLDFL7 START 0
*
*        EXHLOURS PROVIDES THE AMS DEFAULT SCREEN LAYOUT, ALLOCATING
*        TO EACH OF SEVEN DISPLAY FUNCTIONS. THE EIGHTH ENTRY FOR
*        EXHDZZZZ IS MANDATORY , SINCE IT CONTROLS I/O TO THE CRT.
*
*        THREE SCREEN MAPPINGS ARE REQUIRED, ONE SET FOR EACH
*        SUPPORTED SCREEN SIZE.
*
*        EXHL MODULES ARE USED BY EXHAMODS IN RESPONSE TO A MODIFY
*        (LAYOUT= ) COMMAND, AND AT INITIALIZATION TIME FROM THE
*        EXEC CARD PARM FIELD AND/OR THE &LAYOUT OPTION.
*
         EJECT
*        1920 BYTE SCREEN (IBM 3270)
*
         XODSP DA00,2,12,1,80,0  ROOM FOR 22 ENTRIES
         XODSP DQ00,13,14,1,80,2 QUEUE SUMM, 18 ENTRIES
         XODSP DR00,18,19,1,80,1 REPLIES
         XODSP IR00,17,17,1,80,1 INTERVENTION REQUESTS
         XODSP MR00,20,21,1,80,1 MOUNT/AVR REQUESTS
         XODSP OF00,15,15,1,80,1 OFF LINE UNITS
         XODSP ON00,22,24,1,80,1 ONLINE DISKS
         XODSP PA00,16,16,1,80,1 PAGE QUEUE LENGTHS
         XODSP ZZZZ,1,24,1,80,0  DISPLAY I/O
         SPACE 2
*        960 BYTE SCREEN (IBM 2260)
*
         XODSP DA00,2,6,1,80,0   ROOM FOR 10 ENTRIES
         XODSP DQ00,7,8,1,80,2   SUMMARY OF 1  QUEUES
         XODSP DR00,10,10,1,80,1 REPLIES
         XODSP IR00,9,9,41,80,1  INTERVENTION REQUESTS
         XODSP MR00,11,12,1,80,1 MOUNT / AVR REQUESTS
         XODSP OF00,9,9,1,40,1   OFFLINE UNITS
         XODSP ON00,11,12,1,80,1 ONLINE DISKS, OVERLAYS MOUNT SPACE
         XODSP PA00,00,00,0,00,255 NO ROOM FOR PAGE QUEUES       *TSM*
         XODSP ZZZZ,1,12,1,80,0  MANDATORY I/O ROUTINE
         SPACE 2
*        480 BYTE SCREEN (SMALL 3270 OR 2260)
*
         XODSP DA00,1,3,1,80,0   ROOM FOR 6 ENTRIES
         XODSP DQ00,4,4,1,80,2   9 ENTRY QUEUE SUMMARY
         XODSP DR00,5,5,41,80,1  REPLIES
         XODSP IR00,5,5,21,40,1  INT. REQ.
         XODSP MR00,6,6,1,80,1   MOUNT/AVR REQUESTS
         XODSP OF00,5,5,1,20,1   OFFLINE INUTS
         XODSP ON00,6,6,41,80,1  ONLINE DISKS
         XODSP PA00,00,00,0,00,255 NO ROOM FOR PAGE QUEUES       *TSM*
         XODSP ZZZZ,1,6,1,80,0  I/O ROUTINE
         SPACE 2
EXHLEND  DS    0D            FOR SIZE TEST
         SIZER EXHLEND-EXHLDFL7,LAYOUT    TEST SIZE
         END
